column16: Ryan Zimmerman grounds into a force out, shortstop Hanley Ramirez to second baseman Dan Uggla.    Alberto Gonzalez out at 2nd.
Alberto Gonzalez singles on a soft line drive to center fielder Cody Ross.    Willie Harris scores.    Pete Orr to 3rd.
Anderson Hernandez flies out to center fielder Cody Ross.
Wil Nieves out on a sacrifice bunt, pitcher Jesus Delgado to first baseman Mike Jacobs.    Willie Harris to 2nd.
Edwin Maysonet grounds out, shortstop Alfredo Amezaga to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.
Humberto Quintero flies out to center fielder Cameron Maybin.
Michael Bourn grounds into a force out, first baseman Gaby Sanchez to shortstop Alfredo Amezaga.    Hunter Pence out at 2nd.    Michael Bourn to 1st.
